WEBVTT

00:00:26.810 --> 00:00:31.901
između šnicle i moje žene, na primer.

00:00:31.901 --> 00:00:34.906
To jest, ako cenim šniclu,

00:00:34.906 --> 00:00:41.019
ona mi, s druge strane, to ne uzvraća.

00:00:41.019 --> 00:00:44.321
Dok me moja žena zove

00:00:44.321 --> 00:00:46.122
zvezdom svog života.

00:00:46.122 --> 00:00:48.706
(Smeh)

00:00:48.706 --> 00:00:50.662
Samo druga osoba koja želi

00:00:50.662 --> 00:00:53.894
može me smatrati željenim bićem.

00:00:53.894 --> 00:00:55.474
Ja to znam, i zato

00:00:55.474 --> 00:00:57.820
se ljubav može preciznije definisati

00:00:57.820 --> 00:01:02.130
kao želja da budete željeni.